{"tid":1977350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁海文以身作則 以「四小龍時報」嘅名義成功登記做出版界選民","createTime":"2020-04-18T01:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T02:23:12.000Z","uid":41404,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57e14c5364441ab1b01ab7291fecbdb32ec7eccb","tid":1977350,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:52:12.000Z","msg":"申請新登記成為功能界別選民下個月2號就截止喇，民主派喺今屆立法會選舉要成功「搶灘」，攞到35+議席，攻防主戰場就喺功能界別組別嘅議席度。民主黨袁海文一於以身作則，今日以「四小龍時報」成功登記咗做體育、演藝、文化及出版界功能界別團體選民。<br />\n<br />\n阿袁每個月都會派「四小龍時報」畀一眾街坊瞭解嚇區內嘅大小事，呢排仲以「四小龍時報」嘅名義申請咗做報刊發行人嘅牌照，今日一收到牌照，就即刻遞表登記咗做體育、演藝、文化及出版界功能界別團體選民，準備身體力行支持民主黨喺立法會選舉攞到過半議席。<br />\n<br />\n唔單止咁，阿袁仲同八方講，其實「四小龍時報」唔係成功申請到牌照嘅關鍵，報刊發行人嘅牌照係唔會特別審理報刊嘅內容，提醒市民大眾只要有一年或以上嘅商業登記證，就可以申請做功能界別選民，攞多一票話事權咁話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200417/JFHZD4P746EESWUQOGZOLK5EMQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FJFHZD4P746EESWUQOGZOLK5EMQ%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppelznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=bfac9a94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200417%2FJFHZD4P746EESWUQOGZOLK5EMQ%2F&h=50926239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200417/JFHZD4P746EESWUQOGZOLK5EMQ/</a>"},{"pid":"9fadaeaafccc5bc6107ca27933c107de3b1441d8","tid":1977350,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999c6b727f8d96ac7a95f5dd851d8868a834fa26","tid":1977350,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a61dbc0aa5f8ed114da484741fd2fd586541e10","tid":1977350,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1c374a232bef519e0afe91e541ce05e51b7f67b6","tid":1977350,"uid":277060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"師兄算係咁...<br />\n乳鴿其中一個正常人<br />\n<br />\n不過佢係咪又俾條 Big 雲搞到佢無得選九西呀 HGC?"}]}